OBTAIN

Usage: obtain [adjective list] <noun> [named <name>] [within <integer> meter[s]]

Traverse the simulation graph with a retriever configured based on the given
parameters and display everything it retrieves.

If given, *adjective list* is one or more adjectives describing properties the
retrieved objects must have.  If more than one adjective is given, separate
them with commas.

<noun> indicates the type of object to retrieve.

If given, <name> is the name by which the object is known to you.

If given, <integer> is a number of meters to search before stopping.  Note
that this is approximated by link count since distance isn't properly
simulated yet.

See Also: obtain?
